subject: Olympic Games (2010)
Figure Skating
Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: Kim Yu-na was nearly flawless, and became South Korea’s first Olympic champion in figure skating. Mao Asada of Japan took silver and Joannie Rochette of Canada the bronze.
